#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kpat.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KPat (aka KPatience) is a relaxing card sorting game. To win the game a "
"player has to arrange a single deck of cards in certain order amongst each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"KPat (alinome KPatience) estas malstreĉa kartordiga ludo. Por venki en la "
"ludo, ludanto devas aranĝi ununuran ludkartaron en certa sinsekvo inter si."

